1 Open phpMyAdmin
2. Select database
3. clic Export tab
4. choose option Custom
5. Add  :

Add CREATE DATABASE / USE statement
Add DROP TABLE / VIEW / PROCEDURE / FUNCTION / EVENT / TRIGGER statement

6. Export file
7. Add before Create database :

DROP SCHEMA IF EXISTS `platz`;



Example :

--
-- Delete DB
--
DROP SCHEMA IF EXISTS `platz`;

--
-- Database: `platz`
--
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS `platz` DEFAULT CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci;
USE `platz`;
